msgstr "Importar biblioteca"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import a library appending the contained symbols into the current library"
msgstr ""
"Importar una biblioteca añadiendo los símbolos que contiene a la biblioteca "
